text: The Female Boss is the debut studio album by English singer and songwriter Tulisa. It was released on 3 December 2012 via All Around the World and Island Records. The first single "Young" reached number one on the UK charts but the album did not meet the same and received bad reviews. == Tracklisting == ;Notes * The official track listing was confirmed by Play.com on 25 October 2012. ==Charts== Chart (2012) Peak position Irish Albums Chart 55 Scottish Albums Chart 41 UK Albums Chart 35 ==Release history== Regions Dates Format(s) Label(s) Ireland 30 November 2012 CD, digital download All Around the World, Island Records United Kingdom 3 December 2012 ==References== Category:2012 albums Category:Debut albums Category:Tulisa Category:Dance albums Category:Hip hop albums Category:R&B; albums
